{"an4.32:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 4.32 ","an4.32:0.2":"4. Cakkavagga ","an4.32:0.3":"Sangahasutta ","an4.32:1.1":"“Cattarimani, bhikkhave, sangahavatthuni. ","an4.32:1.2":"Katamani cattari? ","an4.32:1.3":"Danam, peyyavajjam, atthacariya, samanattata—","an4.32:1.4":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, cattari sangahavatthuniti. ","an4.32:2.1":"Dananca peyyavajjanca, ","an4.32:2.2":"atthacariya ca ya idha; ","an4.32:2.3":"Samanattata ca dhammesu, ","an4.32:2.4":"tattha tattha yatharaham; ","an4.32:2.5":"Ete kho sangaha loke, ","an4.32:2.6":"rathassaniva yayato. ","an4.32:3.1":"Ete ca sangaha nassu, ","an4.32:3.2":"na mata puttakarana; ","an4.32:3.3":"Labhetha manam pujam va, ","an4.32:3.4":"pita va puttakarana. ","an4.32:4.1":"Yasma ca sangaha ete, ","an4.32:4.2":"samavekkhanti pandita; ","an4.32:4.3":"Tasma mahattam papponti, ","an4.32:4.4":"pasamsa ca bhavanti te”ti. ","an4.32:4.5":"Dutiyam. "}